subject: Football
lead_paragraph: Gabe Le ran for 116 yards and 2 touchdowns to help Carroll College of Montana beat the defending champion Sioux Falls, 17-9, in Savannah, Tenn., for Carroll’s fifth N.A.I.A. title in the last six years.
